Anyway, gotta go kidnap a Greek guy.

15:55.621 --> 15:57.521
Stan, come back!

15:58.691 --> 16:01.216
<i>- Where's my mom and Hercules?
- Mmm, mmm!</i>

16:01.327 --> 16:04.296
I might lose my toes to diabetes,
