- We need to get to the airport.
- You go. I gotta get home.

16:32.691 --> 16:35.159
I got term papers to grade.

16:35.260 --> 16:37.854
Klaus, guess what.
I went online...

16:37.963 --> 16:39.988
and found out
there's a cure for ich.

16:40.099 --> 16:42.192
You can buy it
at any pet store. Look.

16:42.301 --> 16:46.499
A cure! Hooray!
I had no idea.

16:46.605 --> 16:50.598
That is something of which
I am just now learning.

16:50.709 --> 16:52.700
Oh, my God. You knew.

16:52.811 --> 16:54.745
You knew there was a cure for ich.

16:54.847 --> 16:58.146
What? That-That-That-That's crazy.

16:58.250 --> 17:01.344
Why would I infect you
and not tell you there's a cure?

17:01.453 --> 17:03.353
So- So your friends
would shun you...

17:03.455 --> 17:06.891
and you'd be forced to come home early
and spend time with me for a change?

17:09.127 --> 17:12.689
How absurd!
Listen to how crazy absurd you sound.

17:12.798 --> 17:15.925
Do you want to make cookies with me?

17:16.035 --> 17:18.731
That's exactly why you did it!
You're sick.

17:18.837 --> 17:21.305
You're sick!

17:21.406 --> 17:24.069
Get out!
Go back to your world!

17:28.380 --> 17:30.280
Klaus, what's wrong?

17:31.383 --> 17:34.113
Oh, nothing.
It's- It's just...

17:34.219 --> 17:38.246
I haven't felt the touch of another
human being in six years.

17:38.357 --> 17:40.450
Oh, you poor thing.

17:43.996 --> 17:45.964
Fish can't get herpes, can they?

17:47.566 --> 17:49.932
All right.
What's the fastest way to the airport?

17:50.035 --> 17:52.469
