or should I take surface streets?

17:52.571 --> 17:54.471
Surface streets or freeway?

17:54.573 --> 17:57.098
Surface streets or freeway?
Surface streets or freeway?

17:57.209 --> 17:59.109
- Freeway.
- Surface streets!

18:01.747 --> 18:04.215
Damn it!
Come on. It's green.

18:04.316 --> 18:06.807
I need to make this light.
Get off your phone.

18:06.919 --> 18:09.285
I have to-
And now it's red. Oh, bravo. Bravo.

