18:21.333 --> 18:23.267
<i>This isn't a contest.</i>

18:23.368 --> 18:26.599
<i>Fuck you! Fine.
I'll take the shoulder.</i>

18:26.705 --> 18:28.730
<i>Excuse me.
Trying to merge. L-I'm just trying-</i>

18:28.841 --> 18:30.308
<i>Fuck you!</i>

18:41.420 --> 18:43.684
I'm coming, Mama.

18:45.491 --> 18:47.982
Oh, okay.

18:48.093 --> 18:50.391
First time peeing in an airplane.

18:50.496 --> 18:54.398
You're a little nervous.
There's no shame in that. Just relax and-

19:00.472 --> 19:02.633
Sir, may I see your ticket?

19:02.741 --> 19:05.539
Blanket? Blanket? Blanket?

19:05.644 --> 19:08.374
Francine?
But how did you- Freeway!

19:08.480 --> 19:12.075
Stan, this is ridiculous.
You have to leave your mother alone.

19:12.184 --> 19:15.745
