on a deserted island.

19:15.854 --> 19:19.153
<i>Attention, everyone. Let's all give a big opa...</i>

19:19.258 --> 19:22.250
<i>to Betty and Hercules,
who'vejust decided to get married!</i>

19:22.361 --> 19:25.194
<i>- Opa!
- Mmm.</i>

19:25.297 --> 19:27.857
- No.
- You see, Stan?

19:27.966 --> 19:31.663
Look how happy she is. There was a time
when you two needed each other...

19:31.770 --> 19:33.670
but she's moved on...

19:33.772 --> 19:35.933
and you have to do the same.

19:36.041 --> 19:38.202
Let her go.

19:41.413 --> 19:44.211
- Or I can stab him in the neck.
- No!

19:44.316 --> 19:46.045
Don't touch my mommy.

19:47.452 --> 19:49.886
What do you think you're doing, young man?

19:49.988 --> 19:53.924
- Saving you.
- Saving me? I don't need to be saved.

19:54.026 --> 19:56.722
- But, Mama-
- You've been the perfect son...

19:56.828 --> 20:00.764
but I finally have a chance at happiness,
and I'm taking it.

20:00.866 --> 20:02.356
But what about me?

20:02.467 --> 20:05.766
Honey, you're the luckiest guy
in the world.

20:05.871 --> 20:08.169
You have a woman who loves you.

20:08.273 --> 20:10.537
- You?
- No! The wonderful woman...

20:10.642 --> 20:14.009
who's put up with us
for all these years.

20:18.483 --> 20:20.610
Now, I'm gonna need you
to sit back down...

20:20.719 --> 20:24.655
because there's an air marshal
pointing a gun at your head.

20:24.756 --> 20:26.986
Oh, hey. Look, I know I was
about to attempt murder...

20:27.092 --> 20:30.289
but it's cool, because I'm about to
reconcile emotionally with my wife.

20:34.399 --> 20:36.333
A toast to the happy couple.

20:36.435 --> 20:40.166
- And to my number one gal.
- Oh, Stan.

20:40.272 --> 20:42.570
<i>- Betty!
- Oh, that's so strange.</i>

20:42.674 --> 20:44.665
